  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Cabin A </strong>is around 62m² sleeping two to six people. Downstairs there are two sleeping alcoves - one with a single bed and one with a double bed, up on the mezzanine level there are three single beds. The apartment has a well-equipped kitchen, lounge area and one bathroom with WC.</p>
<p><strong>Cabin B </strong>is around 62m² sleeping two to five people, with a double room and a mezzanine level with three single beds. The apartment has a well-equipped kitchen, lounge area and one bathroom with WC.</p>
<p>One linen set with towels is included per person, per week. End of stay cleaning is included.</p>
<p><strong>Cabin facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Lounge area with fireplace</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Terrace with lake views</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Clothes dryer</li>
<li>Kitchenette with oven, stove, microwave, toaster, fridge, tea and coffee making facilities.</li>
<li>Washing machine</li>
<li>Bathroom with shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
